title: Kingfield Neighborhood - South Minneapolis Condo- Close to Uptown
posting_body: ['Modern spacious condo, well maintained, very clean and conveniently located in South Minneapolis, close to uptown.', 'Available March 1st.', 'The condo has a large living room that can accommodate a dining area.', 'The kitchen has updated appliances including a dishwasher.', 'The bedrooms are a nice size; 17x13 and 10x13.', 'The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet (7x7) .', 'The condo itself has abundant storage space; a linen closet, a large coat closet at the entry way and extra storage space outside the condo (inside the building).', 'The condo comes with one assigned off-street parking spot.', 'Laundry facilities are free.', 'Utilities are included with the exception of electric, cable and phone.', 'If you like public transportation, a bus stop is close by.', 'The neighborhood has some great restaurants and coffee shops and convenient access to 35W.', 'No smoking or pets allowed.', "Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'Please email to make an appointment for a showing.']
